room_title: Escape room "Prison Break" by Escape Redding in Redding
room_description: It's 1972 and you have been proven guilty of a crime you did not commit. It's like the system is against you, the options seem slim. Someone sneaks a note into the palm of your hand after the trial, "we will be in touch" signed and stamped by V.A. What is this? The only option is escaping.
